# Hosting & Deployment
- Backend: Deploy Express app with Node.js runtime (Railway, Render, Fly.io, or Vercel)
- Frontend: Deploy React app (Vercel or Netlify)
- Database: Supabase (hosted PostgreSQL)
- Use environment variables for all configuration
- Set up proper CORS for production
- Configure proper error logging
- Use connection pooling for Supabase (handled by client)
